dict.string: MULTI SELECT: Add item to clipboard
${LPASS_BIN} show ${item_id} --${copy_field} --sync=no -c && echo "${copy_field} copied to clipboard" || echo "Error copying ${copy_field} clipboard!"

FILE="${HOME}/.lpass/env"
if [[ -f ${FILE} ]]; then echo "test" sed -i '' '/LPASS_AGENT_TIMEOUT/d' ${FILE} fi
Press ENTER to set agent timeout to '{query}' sec.
Press ENTER to set your username to '{query}'
